Package backend

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Athlete
    Class that creates an Athlete and has a bunch of functionality related to the athlete and the athletes expected and measured haemoglobin levels.
    AthleteGlobinDate
    Class that is mainly used to connect haemoglobin readings with a date for calculating expected haemoglobin levels for athletes, as well as for making the expected and measured haemoglobin levels graphs.
    AthleteLocation
    Class made to store a location together with the number of people at that location.
    AthleteLocationsList
    Class made to create an ArrayList of AthleteLocations.
    AvgHaemoglobinLevel
    Database/calculation class for the AvgGlobinLevelChart.
    CryptWithMD5
    Created by camhl on 19.04.2017.
    CSVReader
    Class made to read CSV-files from a specific map, and split it by a specific value.
    GoogleMaps
    Class made for creating an image of a map for visualising the athletes location in the different athlete pages.
    LocationAdder
    When a new locations is being added trough the CSV-file this class is used to add both the location and a new athlete if the athlete does not already exist.
    RandomPasswordGenerator
    Class made to generate a random password.
    SearchHelp
    Underlaying data-class for the AthleteSearchPanel and UserSearchPanel Cant't be named SearchConnection because it conflicts with something else...
    SendEmail  
    Sport
    Class made make a Sport Object.
    User
    Class that creates a user and has functionality associated with the user.
    UserManager
    Class that is used to manage a user.
    Watchlist
    Class made to create a watchlist of all the athletes that has a higher measured haemoglobin level than they should.
